metadata.name: BINARY [MULTITRACK 8/8] - VOCAL
metadata.description:
This is an audio reactive animation on the VOCAL audio track. 
One out of 8 tracks from the title BINARY by Etienne de Crécy.  
It is a piece from a set of 8 which all together form the complete artwork.

Etienne de Crécy, 2021 

BINARY appears on the album BEATS’N’CUBES released in 2010
